description:
Get hip to this!  On today's episode of You'll Hear It, Peter and Adam analyze Christian McBride's solo on his new groovy tune "Pier One Import."  You can get our podcast on Apple Podcasts, Google Podcasts, Spotify or wherever you get your podcasts.  For more info, check out our website: http://www.youllhearit.com

The theme song for You'll Hear It is Peter Martin's "Emotion in Motion":
https://open.spotify.com/album/2JGW2LrkEQxXHrzldmXs4K

Be sure to subscribe to our channel!  We're uploading a video for each episode of our podcasts, so come back each day to check them out!

Follow us on Facebook, Twitter & Instagram at:
https://www.facebook.com/heyopenstudio
https://twitter.com/heyopenstudio
https://www.instagram.com/heyopenstudio
